                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7460" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1860</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1983 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">涅槃重生：祁连山水泥的数字化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Nirvana Rebirth:The Digital Transformation Journey of Qilian Mountain Cement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷亮，南红兵，文慧鹃，王佳，张靖靖，贾蕊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">甘肃祁连山水泥集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">祁连山水泥；传统制造业；战略变革；数字化转型；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Qilian Mountain Cement; Traditional Manufacturing; Strategic Transformation; Digital Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">水泥行业经过十多年的高速发展，各大水泥企业无序扩张，导致行业产能严重过剩。同时，近年来受房地产市场低迷、基础建设投资乏力、新冠疫情频发等因素影响，使水泥市场形势更加严峻。在物联网、大数据和人工智能等新技术快速迭代的今天，祁连山水泥作为传统制造企业，克服“产能严重过剩、环保政策升级、传统产业重塑”等诸多不利因素，依托新技术赋能企业管理，使传统企业与现代新型技术快速融合。本文通过祁连山水泥数字化转型之路，探索数字经济与实体经济深度融合，推动传统制造业向高端化、智能化、绿色化发展，促进企业提升管理效能，引领制造业数字化发展步伐。同时，通过本案例旨在帮助学生理解企业开展数字化转型的过程、特点和意义，引导学生分析传统制造企业推进数字化转型面临的困难和挑战，并对制造企业数字化转型的方法论进行思考。但新时代、新格局、新理念对传统制造业数字化转型的挑战在不断上升，面对层出不穷的新业态、新模式，祁连山水泥的数字化转型还将面临新的考验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After more than a decade of rapid development, the cement industry has witnessed chaotic expansion by major cement companies, leading to severe overcapacity. At the same time, in recent years, factors such as the sluggish real estate market, weak infrastructure investment, frequent outbreaks of the COVID-19 pandemic, and other factors have made the cement market situation even more severe. In today&#39;s era of rapid iteration of new technologies such as the Internet of Things, big data, and artificial intelligence, Qilian Mountain Cement, as a traditional manufacturing enterprise, has overcome many adverse factors such as &quot;severe overcapacity, upgraded environmental policies, and reshaping of traditional industries.&quot; It has relied on new technologies to empower enterprise management and rapidly integrate traditional enterprises with modern new technologies. This article explores the path of digital transformation of Qilian Mountain Cement, aiming to promote deep integration between the digital economy and the real economy, drive the development of traditional manufacturing industries towards high-end, intelligent, and green transformation, enhance management efficiency, and lead the digital development of the manufacturing industry. At the same time, through this case, the article aims to help students understand the process, characteristics, and significance of digital transformation in enterprises, guide students to analyze the difficulties and challenges faced by traditional manufacturing enterprises in promoting digital transformation, and contemplate the methodology of digital transformation for manufacturing enterprises. However, in the new era, new patterns, and new concepts, the challenges of digital transformation for traditional manufacturing industries are constantly increasing. Faced with emerging new formats and models, the digital transformation of Qilian Mountain Cement will also face new tests.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新管理》、《大数据管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；资源基础理论；动态能力理论；集约增长战略；成本领先战略；SWOT矩阵</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
